Package manager

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Album
    Creates Album object that contains a title, artist, genre, release date, and availability status
    Collection
    Creates a collection object to keep track of all albums that a user contains and help users manipulate their album collection such as finding, adding, deleting , lending, and printing albums
    CollectionManager
    Creates user interface for managing an album by taking in various user commands which perform certain functions
    Date
    Creates a Date object which is relevant for users when storing their albums and its subfields in their collection and ensures validity of a particular album date
    RunProject1
    Runs the album manager
  • Enum Summary

    Genre
    creates Genre object with list of multiple different categories
